ssian leader the next, has made itself impossible to ignore.          Follow Al Jazeera English:","source":"Al Jazeera","url":"https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2026/5/19/neutral-superpower-china-why-putin-visit-to-beijing-after-trump-matters","kafka_timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:52:43.923Z","ingestion_time":"2026-05-19T09:53:00.008Z"}
{"titre":"Child survivor of San Diego mosque shooting describes ordeal","date_publication":"2026-05-19 09:52:44","categorie":"video","contenu":"Child survivor of San Diego mosque shooting describes ordeal A nine-year-old boy who survived the San Diego mosque shooting that killed three people has described seeing ŌĆśbad stuffŌĆÖ. His mother, a refugee from Gaza who came to California two decades ago, gave permission for reporters to speak to her son. Save Share Follow Al Jazeera English:","source":"Al Jazeera","url":"https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2026/5/19/child-survivor-of-san-diego-mosque-shooting-describes-ordeal","kafka_timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:52:44.243Z","ingestion_time":"2026-05-19T09:53:00.008Z"}
